title: Trade Ignite - Free Trading Simulator to Learn Technical Analysis in Stock Market
description:
Trade Ignite is the unique application available for traders in Indian Stock market to practice trading without loosing money. Trade Ignite simulates the trading environment with real data of stocks from the past. User can look at the candle sticks and if any convincing pattern is found he can take the trading decision. Each user gets a starting amount of 100000 to start trading. 

One can purely focus on technical analysis as no news and other stuff is present to disturb the user. For those people who are willing to trade purely based on price action this app will be really useful.

Important features to note are, each chart is of daily time frame, user can track all his trades in the profile page. To adopt trading discipline stoploss is mandated in the trade ignite.
